<l>attoṭu civaṇu māyirat tiṟuti</l>
<l>yotta veṇṇu muṉvaru kālai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the word <foreign xml:lang="ta">ilam</foreign> ' poverty ' is followed by <foreign xml:lang="ta">paṭu</foreign> ' to experience ',</l>
<l>it may remain, in poetry.<note
              place="foot">i.e. <foreign xml:lang="ta">ilam + pāṭu &gt; ilampāṭu</foreign> ' to
          become poor, to suffer poverty '. Cf. Malai-paṭukaṭam 576, <foreign xml:lang="ta">ilampaṭu
          pulavar.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
